===Pronunciation===
*bû(r)ch, /bɜː(r)tʃ/, /b3:(r)tS/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)tʃ|Rhymes: -ɜː(r)tʃ]]

===Noun===
'''birch'''
# any tree falling in the birch family of trees.
# wood taken from the birch tree.
# a stick or rod made from birch wood.

===Verb===
'''birch'''
# to punish with a stick or rod made of birch wood.
# to punish as though one were using a stick or rod made of birch wood.

